                "caption": "Figure 1:From text-only reuse to visual skills.Direct answering solves each visual task as a one-off prompt, while text-only skills can reuse rules but leave spatial conventions implicit.Visual Skillcombines reusable text rules with explicit visual priors, making the visual protocol visible, reusable, and grounded.",
