                "caption": "Figure 2:Visual Skillcapability demo.Visual skills are organized by the visual bottleneck they solve: static skills clarify reusable spatial conventions; dynamic skills write intermediate state back onto the task image, including slide critique and ARC route-state planning; interleaved skills keep reasoning steps adjacent to their visual evidence.",
